      "writtenOn": "2020-11-06T16:54:33Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "No. but i\u0027m not sure what you are asking:\n   not \"non-immediate\" in the Git-parent sense -\u003e NO, \n       because I don\u0027t use Soft dep for to store Git parent-\u003echild relationship.\n   \"non-immediate\" in a sense of \"transitive\" deps -\u003e also NO\n       If this CL has \"CQ-Depend: 123\" and CL 123 has \"CQ-Depend: 456\", the 456 won\u0027t be in the list of SoftDeps of this CL.",
      "parentUuid": "a1179958_f0383c5a",
      "revId": "a4f7c3b435cdfafdc57e31bdce807b83a4b9639c",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
